title: TheNinjaMemoirs
author: l337Ninja
pages:
#- Now this is the story all about how,
My skillz in flips and sneakin upside down.
Slashing foes left and right with a sword of iron...
Heres the story of the legend, the l337Ninja of Orion!
#- In Civ 1.0, born and raised. In Lazuli is where I snuck around most of my days.
Throwing partys, chillin, sneakin around all cool, and smackin up griefers with hoes for being such tools
#- When some HCF who were up to no good, starting causin trouble in my neighborhood. I stole all of their crops and a guy in d got scared.
Next time I came they all were prepared.
#- I whistled for my hoes and planned to book it, but I saw somethin cool and decided to check it

A city of cobble, with ugly to spare.
But somethin was special about this land of lolz and pasta...
I had found my new home in a town called New Augusta!
#- New server map up, time to plan a town and build legit.
But griefers came by and couldnt stand it one bit.

Altorum was the name, cool in both game and fame. But when the griefers came in town, what could I say? I left for the homeland,
#- so far away.

Orions the name, Riches power women its game. l337Ninja's here now, still one and the same.

With P to fuel me up, and hoes to occupy my time,
all thats left is books and a game of Busta Rhyme!
#- TO: Arthreas, winner of the first Annual Ninja Games.
May the odds be ever in your favor -l337Ninja
#- 